@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = my-secret-team-token

### PLAYER SETUP

### Register a new Ship
# First time: Creates the ship
# Subsequent times: Updates the team name (reconnect)
POST {{host}}/ships/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "teamName": "USS Enterprise"
}

### Get My Status
# Returns position, fuel, credits, cargo, etc.
GET {{host}}/ships/me
X-Token: {{token}}

### Configure Ship Systems
# Toggle auto-collection (true = vacuum mode, false = flyover mode)
POST {{host}}/ships/me/config
X-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autoCollect": true
}



### NAVIGATION & SENSORS

### Set Course
# headingDeg: 0=North, 90=East, 180=South, 270=West
POST {{host}}/ships/me/course
X-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetX": 200,
  "targetY": 200,
  "speed": 50
}

### Stop Ship
POST {{host}}/ships/me/course
X-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "headingDeg": 0,
  "speed": 0
}

### Scan
GET {{host}}/scan?radius=300
X-Token: {{token}}

### List Active Missions
# Global list of courier jobs available to everyone
GET {{host}}/missions



### ACTIONS (Refill, Trade, Cargo)

### Refill Fuel
POST {{host}}/ships/me/refill
X-Token: {{token}}

### Unload / Sell Cargo
POST {{host}}/ships/me/unload
X-Token: {{token}}

### Dump Cargo
POST {{host}}/ships/me/dump
X-Token: {{token}}



### WORLD & VISUALIZATION (Frontend / Debug)

### World Snapshot (God View)
GET {{host}}/world/snapshot

### Leaderboard
GET {{host}}/leaderboard